# ASP.NET Core Employee Web API ( Day 14 Practice)

## Overview

This project demonstrates ** Simple Web API Endpoints** using ASP.NET Core MVC.
An employee form is used to create employee records, and API endpoints allow retrieving employee data.

The application stores employee data in **temporary in-memory storage (`List<Employee>`)**.

---

## Features

* Employee creation using an HTML form
* Model Binding using `Employee` model
* Data validation using Data Annotations
* Simple Web API with three endpoints:

  * Create Employee
  * Get All Employees
  * Get Employee By ID

