## Workflow

```
User opens employee form
        ↓
GET /employee/create
        ↓
User submits form
        ↓
POST /employee/create
        ↓
Employee stored in List<Employee>
        ↓
GET /employee → Retrieve all employees
GET /employee/{id} → Retrieve specific employee
```

